## Testing plan

Gates that apply this slice (domain + storage only, no UI):
`build`, `unit-tests`, `constructor-unit-tests`, `impl-log-structure`,
`state-of-world-structure`.

- `build` — `dotnet build Berreman.slnx -c Release` (cwd `Berreman/`).
- `unit-tests` — legacy `BerremanTests` suite (regression; baseline‑gated).
- `constructor-unit-tests` — `OpticalConstructor.Tests` exercises the new
  `PlacementTests.fs`: rest‑pose normals (AC‑A1), default locks (AC‑A2),
  `r2 + R2` additivity (AC‑A3), R3 non‑orthogonality (AC‑A4), emission
  invariant (AC‑A5), catalogue‑kind mapping (AC‑A7), and a placement
  round‑trip + schema‑validation fixture (AC‑A6) added reusing the existing
  `ProjectJsonRoundtripTests` harness.
- `ui-smoke` / `ui-tests` do **not** apply: this slice touches no
  `OpticalConstructor.Ui` or `OpticalConstructor.Ui.Tests` file.

